(120, 1, '2022-09-06 13:20:11', '2022-09-06 13:20:11', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To connect the schemes given by the Government through the Department of Fisheries and various organizations to the fishermen at the field level to discuss the implementation of the schemes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In this way, we are continuously trying to protect the fishermen, coast, coastal area, ponds and rivers by providing services in 856 fishing villages in the state in economic, social, educational and medical terms.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are praying that all of you can join the organization that is providing such selfless services and come forward to provide voluntary services by taking membership from every district, mandal and village in our Andhra Pradesh to protect and develop our people.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"columns\":2,\"linkTo\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-2 is-cropped\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":118,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://mssap.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Screenshot-from-2022-09-06-18-48-11.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-118\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":117,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://mssap.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Screenshot-from-2022-09-06-18-48-34.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-117\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":115,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://mssap.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Screenshot-from-2022-09-06-18-48-56.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-115\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":114,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-