 villages.<br>Tirumala Tirupati Vari Ratha Yatra and Srinivasa Kalyanam are being held. Sri Matsyanarayana Swamy Temple has been constructed on the beach of Narasapuram in West Godavari district with crores of rupees.<br>Apart from that, Tirumala Tirupati Devasthanam has given idols of Lord Venkateswara and built temples in the state.<br><br></li><li><b>Women\'s Economic Self-reliance</b>: In fishing villages, setting up saving and fishing groups and providing financial support to women through the Department of Fisheries, setting up sewing machines and training them. Provided Rs. 25000/- to each group under the financial assistance to 736 groups through Matsyamitra groups. The fishermen women were trained on seaweed cultivation by NFDB. Training was given to women for the management of Mahila Sanghas.<br><br></li><li><b>Self-Employment</b> (Government Schemes): To connect the schemes given by the Government through the Department of Fisheries and various organizations to the fishermen at the field level to discuss the implementation of the schemes. In this way, we are continuously trying to protect the fishermen, coast, coastal area, ponds and rivers by providing services in 856 fishing villages in the state in economic, social, educational and medical terms. We are praying that all of you can join the organization that is providing such selfless services and come forward to provide voluntary services by taking membership from every district, mandal and village in our Andhra Pradesh to protect and develop our people.<br><br></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-09-06 13:40:46', '2022-09-06 13:40:46', '', 8, 'http://mssap.in/?p=138', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
