(319, 1, '2022-09-10 04:11:21', '2022-09-10 04:11:21', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<p><br><strong>Contact:  </strong><br>\n<br><b>UMMADI MAHESH</b> \n<br>PRESIDENT\n<br>+91 7075571411\n<br>\n<br><b>G UMAMAHESWAR</b>\n<br>VICE PRESIDENT\n<br>+91 9441046428 \n<br>\n<br><b>KONDURU LAKSHMANARAO</b>\n<br>GENERAL SECRETARY \n<br>+91 9603409548\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><span style=\"float:right\"></span></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Establishing free 78 tuition centres (Bala Samskara Kendralu) across the state in fishing villages to provide accommodation and education to the college students in 5 places.  Accommodation facilities for hostel students providing in Nellore, Prakasam, Vijayawada</strong>, <strong>Kakinada,  Visakhapatnam.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<p>For women and men who has stopped their education in the middle and want to resume it again, efforts are made to study 10th Class, Inter and Degree through distance education and through Open schools. Through Bala Sanskara Kendras adults are taught to read and write to increase the literacy rate in fishing villages.</p>\n<ul style=\"color: #7a7a7d;\">\n    <li>Bala Sanskara Kendras are being run in 79 villages in 5 districts across the state.</li>\n    <li>31 Centres are in Nellore District and 11 cnetres are in Kavali Mandal.</li>\n    <li>Vidavalur mandal has 12 centres.</li>\n    <li>Ulavapadu mandal has 8 centres.</li>\n    <li>Ongole District has 11  centres, Singaraya Konda Mandal has 4 Centers and Kothapatnam Mandal has 7 Centers.</li>\n    <li>West Godavari District has 17,  Mogalthur Mandal has 10 Centres, Bhimavaram Mandal has 3 Centres and Narasapuram Mandal has 4 Centres.</li>\n    <li>Visakhapatnam District has 10, Bheemili Mandal has 8 and Visakha City has 2 Centres.</li>\n    <li>10 centres in Srikakulam District, 4 Centres in Srikakulam R